<p style="text-align: center;">&#8220;Navajo Nation Poet Laureate Jake Skeets&#8217;s highly anticipated second collection patiently tracks the impacts of climate change on the land and its myriad inhabitants.&#8221;<br />
<em>–</em>From the publisher</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-attachment-id="268064" data-permalink="https://lithub.com/louise-erdich-han-kang-david-streitfeld-and-more-20-new-books-out-today/9781631496349_p0_v4_s1200x630/" data-orig-file="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/9781631496349_p0_v4_s1200x630.jpg" data-orig-size="411,630" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}" data-image-title="Darkology, Rhae Lynn Barnes" data-image-description="" data-image-caption="" data-medium-file="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/9781631496349_p0_v4_s1200x630-196x300.jpg" data-large-file="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/9781631496349_p0_v4_s1200x630.jpg" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-268064" src="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/9781631496349_p0_v4_s1200x630-196x300.jpg" alt="Darkology, Rhae Lynn Barnes" width="196" height="300" srcset="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/9781631496349_p0_v4_s1200x630-196x300.jpg 196w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/9781631496349_p0_v4_s1200x630-39x60.jpg 39w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/9781631496349_p0_v4_s1200x630-33x50.jpg 33w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/9781631496349_p0_v4_s1200x630.jpg 411w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 196px) 100vw, 196px" /></p>
